{"tid":1766294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[噴字手足入] 官逼民反，民不得不反","createTime":"2019-12-02T12:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T20:50:12.000Z","uid":54719,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4543052613eaa3f4b4eba5a9ec48cab2666df010","tid":1766294,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"其實噴字最主要目的都係想喺一、兩句內做到宣傳/解釋的效果，同廢老/淺藍溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就應該用一啲佢地一睇就明既terms/句子<br />\n<br />\n「官逼民反，民不得不反」雖然係老土咗啲，但佢地睇到就會即刻明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋用依句，會直接喺佢地個腦入面連結埋中國以前咁多次暴政下既革命，滿足佢地「中國人」既身份認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，之前見到一啲名人名言都唔錯，不過記得中英對照呀，有啲人會睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道已經有好多人噴過依啲句子，但我意思係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">9成</span></span>都要係依種啊！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」「沒有暴徒，只有暴政」依啲間中一兩句就得，唔洗太多，因為唔夠上述嗰種句子咁efficient<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f7cf840ae287f58ce36a1d94646acc094df15d","tid":1766294,"uid":54719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"connect淺藍，中立撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c62fcbc88e66cb11c0b048fe61cbf90c3e67922","tid":1766294,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"好po推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d052e26aee890975f0acb5f5b3d0a364028e9a","tid":1766294,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"